00:48:15,017 --> 00:48:16,685
-Yes.
-What?

535
00:48:16,769 --> 00:48:18,145
What?

536
00:48:25,819 --> 00:48:27,112
What I'm saying is

537
00:48:28,280 --> 00:48:31,075
don't steal Ji-ung away from me.
He's my friend.

538
00:48:37,206 --> 00:48:38,707
NJ

539
00:48:40,334 --> 00:48:42,044
NJ

540
00:49:10,197 --> 00:49:11,073
Sol-i.

541
00:49:12,241 --> 00:49:15,160
If you take another step,
I won't let you leave.

542
00:49:15,244 --> 00:49:17,288
You have to help me with this.

543
00:49:18,497 --> 00:49:21,959
-I was just passing by.
-You come here every day.

544
00:49:22,042 --> 00:49:24,795
I know, right?
This place is pretty charming.

545
00:49:24,878 --> 00:49:27,089
The owner here is even more charming.

546
00:49:27,172 --> 00:49:29,341
Don't like me.
I don't date younger guys.

547
00:49:29,425 --> 00:49:32,595
Really? Thank you.
You have to keep your word!

548
00:49:32,678 --> 00:49:35,306
Hey, why don't you come in for a minute?

549
00:49:35,389 --> 00:49:36,807
No, I'm not going to help you.

550
00:49:36,890 --> 00:49:39,685
That's not why I want you inside.
Come on in.

551
00:49:39,768 --> 00:49:42,354
-No, I have to go.
-Where are you going?

552
00:49:42,438 --> 00:49:45,274
Hey. Stop bumming around and work.

553
00:49:45,357 --> 00:49:47,109
I had work today,

554
00:49:47,192 --> 00:49:49,069
but Ung suddenly canceled.

555
00:49:49,653 --> 00:49:51,113
He said he's still sick,

556
00:49:51,196 --> 00:49:52,656
so I'm going to check in on him.

557
00:49:54,658 --> 00:49:55,701
He's sick?

558
00:49:55,784 --> 00:49:59,288
Yes. I'm I heard he was all better,
but he says he's sick again.

559
00:49:59,955 --> 00:50:01,624
And he told me not to come.

560
00:50:01,707 --> 00:50:04,251
But, as his manager,
I should go check in on him.

561
00:50:04,335 --> 00:50:06,128
No, you shouldn't go.

562
00:50:06,211 --> 00:50:07,463
Why?

563
00:50:08,339 --> 00:50:11,258
-I'm sure he has a guest.
-A guest? Who?

564
00:50:11,342 --> 00:50:13,886
Never mind. Anyway, you shouldn't go.

565
00:50:13,969 --> 00:50:15,137
Just come here.

566
00:50:15,220 --> 00:50:17,097
-Come on.
-No.

567
00:50:17,181 --> 00:50:19,350
You promised not to do that.

568
00:50:19,433 --> 00:50:20,976
I'm off-limits.

569
00:50:21,977 --> 00:50:24,521
You're such a little brat.

570
00:50:24,605 --> 00:50:27,024
Come over here
before I shower you with scallions.

571
00:50:32,488 --> 00:50:35,074
-Are you leaving?
-Yes. Aren't you?

572
00:50:35,157 --> 00:50:36,950
I'm going to work a little more. Go on.

573
00:50:37,034 --> 00:50:38,035
All right.

574
00:50:43,332 --> 00:50:45,084
Do you have something to say?

575
00:50:46,418 --> 00:50:48,253
Ji-ung, well…

576
00:50:50,923 --> 00:50:52,883
Do you want to join me for dinner?

577
00:50:56,387 --> 00:50:59,348
You have to eat
if you're going to keep working,

578
00:50:59,431 --> 00:51:02,518
and I don't have much to eat at home.

579
00:51:02,601 --> 00:51:03,644
Sure.

580
00:51:03,727 --> 00:51:06,271
Why are you explaining yourself?
Let's go eat.

581
00:51:08,857 --> 00:51:11,235
We could have eaten out.

582
00:51:11,318 --> 00:51:13,779
It's fine. You have to get back to work.

583
00:51:14,571 --> 00:51:15,531
Fine, then.

584
00:51:21,620 --> 00:51:23,914
Stop staring at me and spit it out.

585
00:51:25,499 --> 00:51:27,751
Well, it's…

586
00:51:29,586 --> 00:51:31,296
Are you having a rough time?

587
00:51:31,380 --> 00:51:34,550
Do you want to be transferred
to a different team? Or quit?

588
00:51:34,633 --> 00:51:37,511
I won't let you quit before I do.
You'd better get in line.

589
00:51:39,263 --> 00:51:40,639
It's not that.

590
00:51:40,723 --> 00:51:42,391
Then what is it?

591
00:51:42,474 --> 00:51:44,768
Why do you keep staring at me?

592
00:51:45,936 --> 00:51:47,980
Do you like Ms. Kook, Ji-ung?

593
00:51:52,109 --> 00:51:54,486
Oh, I'm sorry.

594
00:51:54,570 --> 00:51:57,197
That was too personal.

595
00:51:57,281 --> 00:51:59,158
It just slipped out.

596
00:52:00,159 --> 00:52:00,993
I'm sorry.

597
00:52:02,035 --> 00:52:03,328
If you're sorry…

598
00:52:05,622 --> 00:52:07,082
keep this a secret.

599
00:52:07,666 --> 00:52:09,752
I haven't told anyone yet.

600
00:52:16,800 --> 00:52:19,553
Was I that obvious?
I don't want anyone to know.

601
00:52:20,637 --> 00:52:23,390
No, I only noticed
because I watched you carefully.

602
00:52:23,474 --> 00:52:26,101
You should be focused on work.

603
00:52:26,185 --> 00:52:27,561
That won't do.

604
00:52:35,068 --> 00:52:37,613
-It's pretty low, right?
-What?

605
00:52:38,197 --> 00:52:39,907
I'm deceiving my friend

606
00:52:39,990 --> 00:52:42,117
and liking her in secret.

607
00:52:42,868 --> 00:52:45,621
You can't control how you feel.

608
00:52:46,205 --> 00:52:47,456
Are you taking my side?

609
00:52:48,123 --> 00:52:49,958
I guess it's nice to have a junior.

610
00:52:53,337 --> 00:52:54,546
Don't worry.

611
00:52:54,630 --> 00:52:57,883
I'll finish this project without
getting my personal feelings involved.

612
00:53:03,096 --> 00:53:06,141
-I'm ordering chicken!
-What?

613
00:53:06,225 --> 00:53:07,810
I'm going to order chicken.

614
00:53:07,893 --> 00:53:08,977
You're leaving?

615
00:53:27,496 --> 00:53:30,123
I shouldn't spy on other people's phones.

616
00:53:49,810 --> 00:53:51,061
But…

617
00:53:52,104 --> 00:53:54,398
I can't help it
if I accidentally end up seeing it.

618
00:53:55,065 --> 00:53:56,483
It's not like I'm blind.

619
00:53:57,943 --> 00:53:58,944
GU EUN-HO

620
00:54:00,821 --> 00:54:03,866
Ung, I rescheduled

621
00:54:03,949 --> 00:54:06,201
Are you still feeling sick?

622
00:54:06,285 --> 00:54:08,161
And are you sure I don't have to come?

623
00:54:13,667 --> 00:54:15,794
He said he had no plans.

624
00:54:16,378 --> 00:54:18,839
What in the world is he thinking?

625
00:54:36,106 --> 00:54:37,900
Did she really leave?

626
00:54:53,624 --> 00:54:55,375
I don't want to go home.

627
00:55:19,483 --> 00:55:22,653
I never said
you could snoop around my house.

628
00:55:55,060 --> 00:55:57,521
You can't do whatever you want
because we're friends.

629
00:56:03,235 --> 00:56:04,611
What's your plan?

630
00:56:05,696 --> 00:56:06,697
What?

631
00:56:06,780 --> 00:56:08,490
You were waiting for me to come back

632
00:56:08,573 --> 00:56:10,575
so you could spray salt and water on me.

633
00:56:11,159 --> 00:56:12,577
You agreed to do the documentary

634
00:56:12,661 --> 00:56:15,455
just so that you can bully me,
hide from me, and reappear.

635
00:56:16,123 --> 00:56:17,457
Then you kissed me.

636
00:56:18,625 --> 00:56:20,335
And now you want to be friends?

637
00:56:22,421 --> 00:56:24,631
I have no idea what you're thinking

638
00:56:25,298 --> 00:56:26,633
so I want to find out.

639
00:56:27,968 --> 00:56:29,136
I don't have any plans.

640
00:56:31,054 --> 00:56:34,182
I just want us to get along as friends.
What's the problem?

641
00:56:35,434 --> 00:56:36,560
But…

642
00:56:41,231 --> 00:56:43,358
why do I feel like you're lying?

643
00:56:50,574 --> 00:56:52,159
You're so conceited.

644
00:56:53,285 --> 00:56:54,870
I have something I want to hear from you.

645
00:56:55,829 --> 00:56:58,331
Come to think of it,
you never said it to me.

646
00:56:59,958 --> 00:57:01,668
So I want to hear you say it now.

647
00:57:02,252 --> 00:57:03,795
You can keep pretending we're friends.

648
00:57:04,838 --> 00:57:06,673
I'm going to make plans of my own.

649
00:57:08,717 --> 00:57:10,093
Oh, and…

650
00:57:11,219 --> 00:57:13,597
I'm taking this since I won the bet.

651
00:57:15,474 --> 00:57:19,269
Isn't this the amusement park
where we broke up for the fourth time?

652
00:57:21,271 --> 00:57:22,397
I can have this, right?

653
00:57:25,233 --> 00:57:26,735
Just leave.
I'm not letting you stay over tonight.

654
00:57:26,818 --> 00:57:29,029
"Tonight"? Then can I come again
some other night?

655
00:57:29,112 --> 00:57:31,281
You're being so weird. Do you know that?

656
00:57:31,364 --> 00:57:32,657
I was about to go anyway.

657
00:57:35,077 --> 00:57:36,286
After I eat the chicken.

658
00:57:46,338 --> 00:57:47,506
Is it fried chicken?

659
00:57:48,131 --> 00:57:49,091
Hang on!

660
00:58:05,690 --> 00:58:07,692
What are you doing here at this hour?

661
00:58:09,986 --> 00:58:11,530
What are you two doing?

662
00:58:21,665 --> 00:58:24,000
Hello. I'm Choi Ung's friend, NJ…

663
00:58:24,084 --> 00:58:25,502
EPILOGUE

664
00:58:25,585 --> 00:58:27,963
Can I use a fake name?
The company doesn't know I'm doing this.

665
00:58:28,046 --> 00:58:31,383
Can you blur my face? No, wait.
Will that make me look like a criminal?

666
00:58:32,551 --> 00:58:33,969
Let's just start filming.

667
00:58:35,637 --> 00:58:37,180
What do you want to know?

668
00:58:37,764 --> 00:58:39,433
Should I talk about Choi Ung?

669
00:58:40,767 --> 00:58:41,726
This is going to be fun.

670
00:58:48,733 --> 00:58:51,319
But what's going on between you three?

671
00:58:53,238 --> 00:58:55,073
It looks like you three got into a fight.

672
00:58:58,326 --> 00:59:05,333
JUST FRIENDS

673
00:59:27,272 --> 00:59:29,232
What are they up to?

674
00:59:29,900 --> 00:59:31,902
-I like it.
-What?

675
00:59:31,985 --> 00:59:35,197
You're not after some criminal.

676
00:59:35,280 --> 00:59:36,698
Hey, Ung!

677
00:59:40,577 --> 00:59:41,411
Yeon-su.

678
00:59:42,287 --> 00:59:44,748
Wait. Do you want to come up?

679
00:59:45,498 --> 00:59:47,667
I don't want to be friends with Ung.

680
00:59:47,751 --> 00:59:49,336
This is bad.

681
00:59:49,419 --> 00:59:51,004
I guess I was wrong.

682
00:59:52,631 --> 00:59:53,882
I do have a crush on him.

683
00:59:55,926 --> 01:00:00,931
Subtitle translation by: Ju-young Park
